      • percentCorrect

        public double percentCorrect
        The percentage of trials for which the correct output was given. A trial is considered correct if each output is with the range given by the target output value +/- the error margin specified given by TargetFitnessCalculator.FITNESS_ACCEPTABLE_ERROR_KEY.
